{"tid":1603859,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[小小提示] Telegram新功能要識得用","createTime":"2019-09-29T19:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T00:41:48.000Z","uid":286309,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3fe52abae85ba8390b48df9c0eb56fe3dbbf04f0","tid":1603859,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:27:31.000Z","msg":"提提大家，臨近發夢前<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">尤其係前線手足</span></span></span><br />\n記得善用Telegram嗰Schedule Message呀<br />\nSend俾信得過嘅朋友，而且佢地要識得幫手喎<br />\n當message send左俾朋友，首先朋友要confirm聯絡到自己<br />\n聯絡到嘅咪好囉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">假設30mins內聯絡唔到，咁你個朋友就要做嘢啦</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.搵星火／各大律師團隊，確保咬左去邊間狗屋<br />\n2.通知屋企人<br />\n3.朋友親自上屋企清理下啲電腦，相關嘅物品等</span></span><br />\n<br />\n終極<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">4.唔想家人自己被自殺嘅，要朋友同屋企人保持聯繫，為免屋企人有意外發生</span></span>"},{"pid":"ecef3b9cd5bcde9cf3848ca7fb9b95b28838824c","tid":1603859,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:30:29.000Z","msg":"如果你係安全到家／肯定無狗咬啦<br />\n咁就好Dele番個Schedule message.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">附送格式一份<br />\n名字: <br />\n身份證:<br />\n自己電話：<br />\n屋企人電話：<br />\n<br />\n備駐</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"1b8a82b13c272b74d94cc050ec26c77f495b4234","tid":1603859,"uid":399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:47:02.000Z","msg":"係前線邊睇到電話啊咪玩啦"},{"pid":"09e64dca101011a2f7f3177e305e490fa5f39dbb","tid":1603859,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:41:48.000Z","msg":"近日好多手足出事，我唔知呢兩個app係咪真係幫到大家，不過都裝嚟試下啦<br />\nGoogle Trusted Contacts<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.go